## 15. 30-second recap

The PMO has three core functions: **provide structure and governance**, **align projects with strategy**, and **improve delivery efficiency and effectiveness**. These functions work together to make project execution more consistent, more relevant to business goals, and more successful in practice. A PMO therefore improves not only how projects are run, but also how much value they generate for the organization. 

